Package: SVCFit
Title: Calculate Structural Variant Cellular Fraction
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yunzhou", "Liu", , "yliu498@jh.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Yunzhou Liu <yliu498@jh.edu>
Description: Estimates the Structural Variant Cellular Fraction (SVCF) for
    inversions, deletions, tandem duplications, and translocations by
    integrating structural variant calls with allele-specific copy number
    variation and heterozygous SNP data.  Includes a Dirichlet-process
    Gaussian mixture model clustering step and phylogenetic tree inference
    for longitudinal paired samples.
